 have a souvenir. I got it from the music school's vending machine. It's hot melon cider.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":330,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":330,"voiceId":"event166-06-053","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":331}],"windowDisplayName":"Rei","body":"Fufufu, thanks. By the way, what was the name of that song we sang together?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":331,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":331,"voiceId":"event166-06-054","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":330}],"windowDisplayName":"Tae","body":"It's \"Nakana iNa kanai.\" ... Is it weird?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":330,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":330,"voiceId":"event166-06-055","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":331}],"windowDisplayName":"Rei","body":"It's cute... I like it.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":331,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":331,"voiceId":"event166-06-056","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":330}],"windowDisplayName":"Tae","body":"Are you going already?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":330,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":330,"voiceId":"event166-06-057","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":331}],"windowDisplayName":"Rei","body":"Mm-hmm, I can't keep my family waiting. I'm sorry, Hana-chan...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":331,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":331,"voiceId":"event166-06-058","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"(I remember now... That was LAYER I spoke with...)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"event166-06-059","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"(And she was desperately holding back her tears while trying to move forward...)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"event166-06-060","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"(This feels amazing... I've never had so much fun in my life. I wish this moment could last forever...)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"event166-06-061","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"(But each note brings me closer to the end. Just one more phrase... and it'll all be over...)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"event166-06-062","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"(And now... I have to go. Because I want to see what lies ahead...!)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"event166-06-063","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0}],"selectableData":[],"layoutData":[{"type":2,"sideFrom":3,"sideFromOffsetX":0,"sideTo":3,"sideToOffsetX":0,"depthType":0,"characterId":331,"costumeType":"331_event_166_story_01","motionName":"","expressionName":"default","moveSpeedType":0},{"type":2,"sideFrom":7,"sideFromOffsetX":0,"sideTo":7,"sideToOffsetX":